Nicki Minaj known as the Queen of Rap, released the art cover of her highly anticipated album by the legendary Mert and Marcus which she has regarded as her greatest work to date. The album which will be Minaj’s fourth studio album has already released two singles in early April Chun-Li and Barbie Tingz. Nicki-Minaj ‘Queen’ Album Cover Photo credit HighNobiety The album titled Queen which was originally set to be released on 15th June 2018 was pushed back to 10th August 2018. Set to start a revolution, Nicki has been constantly hinting about its lyrics in several tweets where she addresses women standing for their rights and knowing their worth.   